title: Jenkins and Jonez - Aaron Rodgers Is Gone and Grayson Allen Needs To Be
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Aaron Rodgers Is Gone and Grayson Allen Needs To Be
description:
The guys award the Booger Boy of the Week to Grayson Allen for his flagrant foul against Alex Caruso, discuss every corner of the internet uniting against Aaron Rodgers, debate whether it’s SportsCenter’s place to tweet jokes about Russell Westbrook, and do some macaque talk.
